headline: HERSHEY'S Milk Chocolate with Caramel Bar Brings the Ooey, Gooey Drip to Summer
summary: Just in time for summer, there's a new treat in town: HERSHEY'S Milk Chocolate with Caramel bar. This delicious twist on the iconic HERSHEY'S Milk Chocolate bar adds new texture with a luscious caramel center to the classic – making snacking even sweeter, especially when there's a campfire around.
